  achievementSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 4607e1a10c000e242b14fcc588616d5d, type: 3}
  confettiEffect: {fileID: 957166842}
  placeNames:
  - ' christ church'
  - ' Kangra Fort'
  - HPCA Stadium
  - ' Gyoto Monastery'
  - Rock Temple
  descriptions:
  - Christ Church, located in Shimla, is one of the oldest churches in North India.
    Built in Neo-Gothic style during British rule, it is known for its beautiful
    stained-glass windows and peaceful atmosphere. The church stands as an iconic
    landmark on the Ridge and reflects colonial-era architecture and history.
  - Kangra Fort is one of the oldest and largest forts in the Himalayas. Built by
    the Katoch dynasty, it has witnessed centuries of battles and rulers. Located
    between two rivers, the fort offers historic ruins, ancient temples, and panoramic
    views of the Kangra Valley.
  - HPCA Stadium in Dharamshala is one of the most scenic cricket stadiums in the
    world. Surrounded by the Dhauladhar mountains, it hosts domestic and international
    matches. Its stunning location and modern design make it a famous sports and
    tourist attraction in Himachal Pradesh.
  - Gyoto Monastery is a renowned Tibetan Buddhist monastery located near Dharamshala,
    Himachal Pradesh. Established to preserve the traditions of the Gelug school
    of Tibetan Buddhism, it is famous for its monks' unique throat chanting and spiritual
    teachings. Surrounded by the scenic Himalayan landscape, the monastery serves
    as a center for meditation, learning, and cultural preservation, attracting visitors
    from around the world.
  - Aghanjar Mahadev Temple, often known as the Rock Temple, is a sacred Hindu shrine
    located near Khanyara in Dharamshala, Himachal Pradesh. Dedicated to Lord Shiva,
    the temple is surrounded by natural rock formations, flowing streams, and lush
    greenery. According to local beliefs, the site has spiritual significance and
    offers visitors a peaceful environment for worship, reflection, and experiencing
    the region's natural beauty.
  images:
  - {fileID: -810227577, guid: 927e6c5a885ab5d438bc98c323706eb4, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 980523577, guid: 4be65da3757820142a37b4d58f3e1b44, type: 3}
